snippet.title: Toby Grotz Explores the Aether Theory and Its Applications
snippet.description:
Srinivasan's Eclipse Experiment and its Implications for Aether Theory

Gopalakrishnan  Srinivasan Performed an experiment during a total solar eclipse in India on the 15th of January, 2010.  The purpose of the experiment was to verify the principles derived in an alternate theory on the structure of the Universe, whereby space is identified as a medium with defined properties, whereas in Physics, scientists hold the opposite view that it is vacuous and empty.  The results of this experiment and methods will be discussed during this presentation.

An attempted replication of the experiment was performed in Wisconsin on April 8, 2024.  Methods and results from this experiment will be discussed.
G. Srinivasin also built and demonstrated and over unity generator based on his theories and understanding of the ancient Vedic Texts of India.  Video and diagrams will be presented.

snippet.title: Robert Haralick Introduces Water and Ion Cyclotron Resonance
snippet.description:
Beginning in the early 1960‚Äôs there was experimental work suggesting that
biological systems could be influenced by magnetic fields. At that time some thought that there was a direct influence of magnetic fields on chemical equilibrium or the rate of reactions. But there was no theory suggesting why magnetic fields would influence chemical equilibrium or rate of reaction. There were also experimental reproducibility issues.

By 1985 there was significant experimental evidence that low frequency
magnetic fields were indeed influencing living cells. Liboff hypothesized that
the effects could be explained by Ion Cyclotron Resonance (ICR). The math behind the ICR effect and the experiments that validated Liboff‚Äôs hypothesis are discussed. The unjust criticism it received is  reviewed and some of the reasons why there were initial reproducibility issues is revealed.

The ionic current phenomena of Liboff and Zhadin in the context of ICR experiments is examined while the quantum electrodynamic theory (QED) explains the effect. The QED theory leads to basic understandings that
include (1) water is a two phase system, the previously unknown phase being
water coherence domains, (2) ions in water are not in Brownian motion, but
move in coherent laminar flow. There are other properties as well that are
not relevant to the ICR discussion.

Experimental issues in creating the DC magnetic field and the AC magnetic field required by ICR are reviewed . Finally, some of the initial experimental results are described.

The Wet Cell is an electro-magnetic battery which is designed to carry specific vibrations into the body. It is an upright wet battery containing a mild acid solution. Two 14" poles (one made of nickel and the other of copper) suspended in the battery solution create a potential between them. This in turn produces a radio wave which is a carrier wave that picks up and delivers the vibration of the element contained in a separate solution jar. The solution jar is a 4-oz. wide mouth jar located on the nickel side of the circuit. Cups and wires connect the individual to the battery and solution jar. Thus Cayce‚Äôs effective method to induce a specific vibration into the body without the inherent dangers associated with ingesting the physical substance, also provided a means for controlling the dosage as well as directing it into a specific region.

An advocate of America‚Äôs most beloved and documented sensitive Edgar Cayce, Phil Thomas had developed and tested the Cayce bio-magnetic battery designed to regenerate nerve tissue. At this time,  Phil is finally ready to pick up where he left off 25 years ago.  Taking into consideration the Cayce readings suggested that this modality could address some 150 different degenerative disorders, one can only hope the timing is right for this concept to finally see the light of day.

snippet.title: Tom Martens Unveils NOEC Patent
snippet.description:
Tom's patented invention is the Nitric Oxide Exchange Chamber (NOEC).  In a modified 2017 Ford Fusion, it removed all of the Hydrocarbons, all of the Carbon Monoxide, all of the Nitric Oxide and lowered the Carbon Dioxide from 12 percent 8 percent from the exhaust. There was even more oxygen coming out of the exhaust than going in!

The Nitric Oxide and hydrocarbons are created when the air in the NOEC (chamber) is exposed to sparks coming from the spark plugs. The air in the chamber then flows through the magnetic fields of the 3 GMX magnets.  The magnetic fields cause the hydrocarbons to attract oxygen before combustion causing better combustion.

snippet.title: Paul Finman Inspires STEM with Drones!
snippet.description:
There is a need to excite and interest young minds in real STEM education, innovation, and hardware development and test. Historically, every generation's interest in technology is inspired by an emerging technology. In the early 1900s it was radio... by the 50s it was hotrods, followed by muscle cars. Soon this was followed by computers... Today, the hot new tech frontier is drones!

Drone design and construction combines a number of technologies ranging from communication to propulsion. This can be facilitated by STEM education, 3D printing of drones, and experimentation in physics with low cost hardware and software.  This presentation examines current state of drone technology and what is available to garage inventors...

I was fortunate that my father was an engineer, he had a shop, and he let me work with his tools and equipment at a young age.  He also bought me somewhat dangerous chemicals, I was allowed to have knives and a BB gun, and I could ride horses that at times would throw me (luckily only bruises and no broken bones). Today, the challenge is to provide an opportunity to embrace a culture that stimulates young minds.  This is a first step!

snippet.title: Max Fomitchev-Zamilov Explores Microscopic Thermonuclear Fusion
snippet.description:
To support Dr. Fomitchev-Zamilov Work check out: 
https://wefunder.com/maximus.energy

There is a nearly universal consensus that inexhaustible fusion energy will power our future. Deuterium fusion fuel from water is cheap with 10 mg of deuterium equal to a barrel of oil! The radiation is entirely contained within the reactor and ceases when the reactor is turned off. The reactor does't emit CO2 or other pollutants and does not produce nuclear waste requiring remediation. Our objective is to revolutionize power generation with compact, inexpensive thermonuclear fusion reactors.

Nuclear fusion does not have to cost billions and require decades to develop. Conventional approaches to fusion are very difficult and very 
expensive using extremely hot plasma. Using magnetic confinement, plasma is created and kept in place using super-strong magnetic fields. With inertial confinement, extremely hot plasma is created and kept in place by compressing a solid fusion target using super-strong lasers. 

Our approach is different. We rely on the nature of collapsing bubbles for containment. We are expanding and collapsing nanobubbles in fluids using

snippet.title: Bill Alek Makes Star Trek Physics Real!
snippet.description:
Back in the late 1990‚Äôs, energy researcher Tom Bearden lectured about a flaw he discovered when Oliver Heaviside applied vector mechanics to simplify James C. Maxwell‚Äôs Electromagnetic (EM) Equations originally written in quaternion mathematics. This classical solution provided by vector mechanics shows that when the cross product of two opposing vectors (q x q) is calculated, the resultant simplified wave function shows an empty zero-vector, which has no internal structure. Tom shows that using Maxwell‚Äôs original quaternion mathematics, the same zero-vector is not empty, but has complex internal structure that simultaneously produces an EM Transverse Scalar Wave function and a local Anti-Gravitational Scalar Wave function. 

This lecture will show that Tom‚Äôs analysis is correct and the output Scalar Wave functions with complex internal structure is produced using what is called a Phase Conjugate Mirror or PCM transformer operating in resonant mode. Also called a PCM Resonator, it outputs an EM Transverse Scalar Wave function that is time-reversed, which in turn, increases the overall output efficiency of the circuit. This amazing scientific breakthrough in electromagnetics will lead to the development of power systems that can have efficiencies greater than 100%. Examples of PCM Resonators includes Nikola Tesla‚Äôs Magnifying Transmitter, Floyd Sweet‚Äôs Space Quanta Modulator, Stanley Meyers Water Car and William Alek‚Äôs Split-Flux Transformer.

snippet.title: Charlles Bohdy Reveals NanoPlasma Spa Technology!
snippet.description:
Targeting the hypoxic tumor microenvironment has a broad impact in cancer epigenetics and therapeutics. Oxygen encapsulated nanosize carboxymethyl cellulosic nanobubbles were developed for mitigating the hypoxic regions of tumors to weaken the hypoxia-driven pathways and inhibit tumor growth. We show that  hypomethylation in hypoxic regions of a tumor can be reverted to enhance cancer treatment by epigenetic regulation, using oxygen nanobubbles in the sub-100 nm size range, both, in vitro and in vivo. Oxygen nanobubbles were effective in significantly delaying tumor progression and improving survival rates in mice models. Further, significant hypermethylation was observed in promoter DNA region of BRCA1 due to oxygen nanobubble (ONB) treatment. The nanobubbles can also reprogram several hypoxia associated and tumor suppressor genes such as MAT2A and PDK-1, in addition to serving as an ultrasound contrast agent. Our approach to develop nanosized oxygen encapsulated bubbles as an ultrasound contrast agent for methylation reversal is expected to have a significant impact in epigenetic programming and to serve as an adjuvant to cancer treatment.

snippet.title: James Sorensen Explores Galaxy Creation with Electricity
snippet.description:
Creating Galaxies with Electricity
Cosmologists believe there is no electricity in Space.  Any initial charge distribution would have neutralized many billions of years ago.  This leaves cosmology with one force to explain our universe - gravity.

Gravity is thought to be the result of mass - the more mass the more gravity.  When we look into space we see objects that have more gravity than can be explained with their calculated mass.  Black Holes were conceived of to explain missing mass found at the center of galaxies.  Dark Matter was conceived of to explain the behavior of galaxies.  Dark Energy was created to explain the suspected acceleration of the expansion of the Universe.  Black Holes, Dark Matter and Dark Energy are all invisible, undetectable forms of matter that cannot be found or studied in a laboratory.   This has resulted in a cosmology where ordinary matter makes up only 4% of the universe.  The remaining 96% of the universe cannot be detected or directly observed.

The Electric Universe theories propose that the primary force which defines our universe is electricity, not gravity.  Electric Universe theorists like Winston Bostick and Anthony Peratt have shown that galaxies can be described using the well-known equations for electro-magnetism.  This is the same mathematics used by engineers to create our modern world of generators, electric motors, communications, power distribution.                                                                       
This presentation will show how electricity forms spiral barred galaxies.

snippet.title: West Plischke Reveals the Plischke Generator!
snippet.description:
The Plischke Generator (aka Infinite-Range Nucleus ARC)  is a solid-state unified power system designed to convert the potential energy stored within permanent magnets into electricity. It increases the rate of change of magnetic flux within the circuit using an array of electromagnets and permanent magnets that interact in concert to enhance the overall magnetic flux within the circuit as the electromagnets oscillate intensity. The unified system design recovers the input power to the electromagnets and the additional magnetic flux provided by their interactions with the permanent magnets by means of electromagnetic induction, adding the EMF produced by their interactions, effectively recovering the input EMF, and collectively producing more electricity than what is required for input power.

This is a solid-state fuel-free fully-autonomous energy source that doesn‚Äôt rely on a separate power source or battery to function. The system sends a fraction of the power it produces back to itself as input power. This device demonstrates excess energy generation while remaining consistent with the fundamental principles of physics. Producing more power output than the energy it requires to operate. The surplus of energy to draw from is a result of the energy contained within the system itself. Energy has not been created, the potential energy stored within the permanent magnets is accessed, adding energy to the system.

This is not to be misunderstood as a hypothetical perpetual motion machine that is suppose to operate indefinitely without input power. On the contrary, this system requires input power which will be explained during the presentation of the first of its kind, a unified fully-autonomous power system.  This device will be able to replace the batteries used in electric vehicles, while a microversion can power biomedical devices. The only constraints are in your imagination!

snippet.title: Isaiah Ritchey Explains the Searl Effect Generator!
snippet.description:
My device is precisely modeled after the Searl Effect Generator device.   John Searl is known all over the world as the inventor of the Searl Effect Generator.  This is a magnetic device, consisting of a series of rings or also called ‚Äúplates‚Äù.  And a number of cylindrical rollers consisting of the same type of elements as in the stator.  My system at this moment uses a series of sophisticated pulsed electromagnets that generate the continual motion of magnetized rollers around magnetized rings.  The magnetic field is holding the rollers tightly to the copper plate, at the same time the electrons moving through layered elements are collected and compressed on the surface of the copper plate lifting the roller and creating the space between the roller and the plate.  This is the Searl Effect, the intersection of two magnetic fields creating a magnetic wave. My generator uses perpendicular magnetic fields located on the rollers and stator rings to create a wave pattern.   
 John Searle designed a generator using magnetic fields to induce a flow of electrons from the neodymium core through a system of rotating magnetized components. So that those electrons would be collected, compressed, used and recycled when the magnetic forces were in motion.  My device contains all the nearly identical elements as the original device he built, and is one the best replicas to ever exist.

snippet.title: Thomas Valone PhD Recounts IRI's Battle Against Suppression
snippet.description:
Starting a public life in 1999, Integrity Research Institute (IRI) became headline news in Science, Science and Government, Village Voice, and other media when its first Conference On Future Energy (COFE) was scheduled for the US State Department but labeled ‚Äúfringe‚Äù and ‚Äúpseudoscience‚Äù with ONE cold fusion speaker from Los Alamos Labs. It was all downhill from there as even Nature magazine broadcasted, ‚ÄúUS State Department Gets Cold Feet on Cold Fusion‚Äù in March, 1999 and the Department of Energy and Commerce also refused to host the conference. 

Getting fired for just trying to have COFE at the Commerce auditorium, I received a six year ‚Äúvacation‚Äù termination, allowing me to finish my PhD in Engineering with a thesis on zero point energy usage. With such notoriety, IRI was emboldened to subsequently pursue research into the scientific integrity of emerging energy, propulsion, and bioenergetics with many books, summary reports, DVDs, and conferences up to COFE12 on Zoom and YouTube in 2020. This slideshow will trace the history of IRI, some of its inventions, research projects, and the ‚ÄúBest of COFE 1-12‚Äù all of which was just archived onto ‚ÄúThe Key‚Äù, a 16 GB flash drive project available free to IRI Members and for sale to the general public.  

Contact Info:
Thomas Valone, PhD, PE
President - Integrity Research Institute
5020 Sunnyside Ave Ste 209, Beltsville MD 20705

snippet.title: Ralph Suddath Highlights Critical Water Technology
snippet.description:
Water Water Everywhere...

From ancient times to the present, a shortage of pristine water has been a serious problem. Even Tesla who nearly died from cholera (a water borne disease) commented on the need for pure water. His ozone generator was promoted as a way to disinfect water!
 
A century later... Ralph Suddath has developed a number of water rejuvenation technologies... many for personal use. Here, he will spend a little time reviewing some of his devices available today! snippet.title: Rory Turnbull presents Integrative Landcare system
snippet.description:
The Integrative Landcare system was created as an interdisciplinary approach between conventional and alternative agriculture and landscaping to bridge the most effective and efficient practices and concepts. By combining the precision, performance and scalability of conventional practices with the ethics, crop quality and sustainability of alternative programs, the benefits associated with any individual methods can be greatly increased. This provides a cost, labor and energy efficient means to create drought-resistant, disease-suppressive and ecosystem promoting soils, that support peak crop performance and quality without excessive or toxic inputs.

Integrative Landcare is a double entendre being it‚Äôs an integrative approach between conventional and alternative landcare sciences, as well as in it‚Äôs intended application towards a reintegration of and with the earth‚Äôs natural systems. The biosphere, lithosphere, hydrosphere and atmosphere are all connected globally through biogeochemical cycles which provide substances and processes which are essential for the basic activity of all earthly life as we know it. The carbon, hydrogen, oxygen, nitrogen, phosphorus, and sulfur cycles are only the most well known of a growing list. These biogeochemical cycles have been greatly dismantled through human activity, but can also be repaired and reconnected through such.

By healing our relationship with the earth we can heal the relationships with ourselves.Thus, the Integrative Landcare system was developed after years of researching conventional science and traditional wisdom, in aims to provide quality resources and practical education to help as many as possible achieve sustainable, consistent, and effective land management practices. Through honest adherence to the core sciences - biology, chemistry and physics ‚Äì many beneficial aspects and quintessential principles of some of the most effective disciplines have been identified, amalgamated, and incorporated into this simple and open system.

snippet.title: Michael Crosswhite: Beyond the Bedini Motor
snippet.description:
Off-Grid power for blackouts & other emergencies!
The Bedini motor patented by John Bedini has been around for many years with thousands, possibly millions of replications. Now we need to go beyond the toy stage and make a useful tool. With increasing power outages across the US for various reasons, it is becoming necessary to have an off-grid power supply to charge phones/ tablets/ radios/ emergency equipment. I will show the general construction of a Bedini motor, how it works, demonstrate its operation, demonstrate processes to increase the basic operation, and demonstrate advanced extraction of energy from the environment that also demonstrates Tesla‚Äôs one wire energy process. Demonstrations include:
1. Four simple components of the Bedini circuit.
2. The basic operation of the Bedini motor.
3. Increase the motor efficiency and output.
4. Energy flow from the environment.
5. Batteries charging by the Bedini motor.
6. Tesla‚Äôs One Wire energy process.
7. How to multiply the energy output.
I will demonstrate how to charge Li-ion battery banks, non-rechargeable alkaline batteries, rechargeable batteries, car batteries and more. I want to show that anyone can understand, build, and use this valuable technology with hand tools and a soldering iron in their own backyard for just a few dollars!!!

snippet.title: Replicating Tom Bearden‚Äôs SCALAR WAVE Technology
snippet.description:
Back in the late 1990‚Äôs, energy researcher Tom Bearden lectured about a flaw he discovered when Oliver Heaviside applied vector mechanics to simplify James C. Maxwell‚Äôs Electromagnetic (EM) Equations originally written in quaternion mathematics. This classical solution provided by vector mechanics shows that when the cross product of two opposing vectors (q x q) is calculated, the resultant simplified wave function shows an empty zero-vector, which has no internal structure. Tom shows that using Maxwell‚Äôs original quaternion mathematics, the same zero-vector is not empty, but has complex internal structure that simultaneously produces an EM Transverse Scalar Wave function and a local Anti-Gravitational Scalar Wave function. 

This lecture will show that Tom‚Äôs analysis is correct and the output Scalar 
Wave functions with complex internal structure is produced using what is called a Phase Conjugate Mirror or PCM transformer operating in resonant mode. Also called a PCM Resonator, it outputs an EM Transverse Scalar Wave function that is time-reversed, which in turn, increases the overall output efficiency of the circuit. This amazing scientific breakthrough in 
electromagnetics will lead to the development of power systems that can have efficiencies greater than 100%. Examples of PCM Resonators includes Nikola Tesla‚Äôs Magnifying Transmitter, Floyd Sweet‚Äôs Space Quanta Modulator, Stanley Meyers Water Car and William Alek‚Äôs SplitFlux Transformer.

Instead, he made a conscious decision to become totally responsible for his own health, and began to look to the past for health care solutions.

In his search, Wayne first investigated the work of Royal Rife and the Rife microscope. Next came Wilhelm Reich with his devices. Finally, Wayne focused his attention on the ideas and technology of Nikola Tesla. It was the inspiration of Nikola Tesla, combined with his own search for optimum health and immunity from disease that led to Wayne‚Äôs creation of Silver Wain Water. snippet.title: Steve's Place... Thad Mauney PhD - Frequency Based  Technologies... Past to Present
snippet.description:
Frequency Based  Technologies... Past to Present

From ancient times to the present, various tones or frequencies have been applied to expedite healing. The modalities are too diverse to cover in a short discussion, but it is interesting to take a brief overview of their history from ancient times to the present.

All around the earth people have built resonant structures. These are broadly spoken of as sacred sites but part of their sacred use may have been for healing, so we can look at what frequencies they might have amplified and how we now might access that healing support. With both physical (musical) instruments and electronic devices we can now produce a vast array of sonic and electrical vibrations available for use when we need healing, but that purpose is overwhelmed by vibrations emitted for other purposes.

So we will spend a little time reviewing just a small portion of the history of healing vibrations in order to give a perspective on how we can use readily available frequency equipment to take care of ourselves, friends, and family. Then we can explore a little of what is still unknown about how those frequencies work and what kind of research might help clarify that so we can make the techniques even better.

snippet.title: John Washenko (1947 -2021)  Memorial
snippet.description:
John Washenko (Apr 1,1947  -  Oct 7, 2021) 

On October 7,  2021, we lost a vital member of our community... John Washenko! John is most familiar to those who have attended the ExtraOrdinary Technology Conferences over the years. During the conferences, John managed our conference bookstore and brought order out of chaos... as a volunteer! This year was particularly stressful as many of our regular volunteer staff was absent due to COVID. John cheerfully took up the slack... because he was that kind of man!
 
For the past 20 years, John travelled the country with me as we went from conference to conference representing TeslaTech. He really liked meeting new people. Additionally, he enjoyed attending the presentations and letting me know who were good candidates for our show. Often he would go convince them to put in an abstract or submit an article for the magazine ExtraOrdinary Science & Technology. 
 
John was a man of faith. Even while manning the table and introducing people to the world of Tesla, he found time to spread the word of his Mormon faith. While there were aspects I disagreed with, we did not let that get in the way of our longstanding friendship. Too often today, it seems that society has lost the art of agreeing to disagree and build a foundation on the ideals we agree on. John had that knack... and he was a true friend that constantly reached out to help others. 
 
For example, I lost my beloved dog and constant companion, Dozer, the night before I had to leave for the Roswell 70th anniversary. John had to drive most of the way as my eyes were filled with tears. My heart was wrenched with pain and I swore I would never get another dog as it was just too painful. During the drive, John told me that dogs love unconditionally, and I should never deny that love. A month later, God saw fit to place a couple of more dogs in my path... and remembering John, I took them in. 
 
John has left us too early... and quite unexpectedly. He died in a rollover accident while on a trip to help a friend with some construction work. They were pulling a trailer and the trailer got loose and flipped their vehicle. John died instantly leaving behind his family wife JoAnn, his children, and his canine companion Rosie. I am sure Rosie is sitting by the door faithfully, patiently waiting for John to get home.

snippet.title: Steve's Place Live w/ Victor Sagalovsky
snippet.description: The story of deuterium depletion is the story of greatest discovery in biology as it affects human health and longevity.  Deuterium is one of the three isotopes of hydrogen - the simplest element and first on the Periodic Table. Deuterium has a neutron whereas common hydrogen does not, and this makes it twice the mass of Protium. This characteristic makes deuterium a biological problem. Both common hydrogen and deuterium combine with oxygen to form water molecules, H2O for normal water and HDO, the D being deuterium, also known as Heavy Water. Deuterium is present in all water (also in all our food that feeds on water) at varying concentrations which have steadily increased over time. There are about 6 drops (150 ppm) of deuterium containing water molecules in every liter of water on Earth.

Both questions may have the same answer related to stopping the flow of gravity and inertia. This seminar will give you a theory of how this all works 
at the particle level.

If such processes existed, they would have the effect of reducing the weight of an object. Gravity Cloaking would stop the effects of both gravity and inertia. I don‚Äôt believe it is theoretical or hypothetical, but that it has been done for thousands of years. 

To understand gravity cloaking, you need an understanding of gravity and 
inertia. When Issac Newton discovered gravity, he called it a natural 
attraction objects have for one another. There were two ideas for that natural attraction, gravity is a force that pulls or gravity is a particle that pushes. We will be discussing gravity as a push. So, for gravity to be a particle that pushes, an atom would have to have gravity particles going to it and through it. If you stop the flow of gravity, you would stop the effects of gravity. Our new atomic model (the key ring atom) allows us to demonstrate how 
to stop the flow of gravity through the key ring atom. While I believe there

snippet.title: Steve's Place Live w/ Robert Plotke
snippet.description:
Mind-Interface Technologies...
Methods that Link Mental-Intention with Practical Application

For millennium societies have sought through mental training the control of their physical environment.  The goal was to seek ever higher planes of enlightenment/consciousness and control. Research efforts in the past decades sought to prove that the mind could influence the physical world directly. These studies consistently proved at a statistically significant level that the mind can influence the physical world directly. Interchange Laboratories similarly researched mental influence on a signal uniquely produced by subatomic electron streaming. 

In one experiment, 48 participants intended to influence a virtual drum on a computer screen.  Participants were requested to fill up the drum as much and as long as possible.  The drum was controlled by the FFT (fast Fourier transform) percent increase or decrease in power at 4 Hz.  The FFT was calculated using continuous and consecutive 10 second data sampling for 5 minutes with 5 mental-intention and 5 non-intention trials for each participant. 

Data Analysis: An ANOVA between intend and non-intend trial FFT percent power data was performed, intend N=387,791 and non-intend N=390,567.  There was a statistically significant difference in trial 2 between the intend and non-intend FFT percent power at 4.00 Hz. with a non-intend mean of 1.71451% and intend mean of 1.72700%, an F of 40.270 and p=0.000. This research confirmed that mental-intention can alter the physical state of mater. These results were encouraging and motivated Interchange Laboratories to continue technological advancements including Plasma based and electronic based capacitive subatomic produced signals, with development of processing techniques that detected greater signal coherence, leading to present real time control application metrics.

snippet.description: Healing of the physical body involves a complex orchestrated progression of biochemical phases which effects multiple cell types and a variety of signaling pathways. Although the standard biomedical model states these changes are controlled by biochemicals, the Quantum healing model proposes that bioenergy is the underlying regulator. Since there are many types of bioenergy, the process becomes complex, but ultimately involves balancing the different energies in the body, whether they be electromagnetic or quantum. It has been further proposed that the link between the energetic body and the physical body is DNA and that diseases are caused by imbalances in the energetic blueprint of the DNA molecule. To validate this quantum healing model, the effects of different forms of subtle energy, focusing on longitudinal scalar waves, on the energetic (electrical) properties of DNA has been assessed experimentally using human DNA in-vitro. The focus of this original research has been to determine which forms of subtle energy resonate best with the DNA and which frequencies best change its electrical properties.

snippet.title: Steve's Place LIVE! with John Brandenburg
snippet.description:
The War of the Singularity, the human race is canceled .... 
A new science fiction novel involving space travel and the Mars and Asteroid Belt colonies of the future. 

In the future, fusion power has solved the energy/climate problem, controlled gravity has allowed colonies to be safely established on the Moon,  Mars and the asteroids.  Life extension technologies have done away with both male and female menopause and a broad spectrum cure for cancer has been found.  Room temperature superconductors are used in many applications, and superconducting optical computing has greatly expanded computer power. However, all is not well with the human race -it cannot seem to stay out of trouble.

Computing science in the area of AI ( Artificial Intelligence) and robotics has also advanced sufficiently in this future as to produce a series of conscious cybernetic entities called ‚ÄòCybercons‚Äô whose raw intelligence first equals and then exceeds that of human beings. Therein lies the root of the central conflict of the novel. Consciousness arose in nature as a neural architecture that enhanced survival of the organisms that possessed it. Self-awareness led to enhanced self-preservation and the result that the genes that produced this effect were passed on more successfully to following generations. So it occurs that in creating a self aware entity of superhuman intelligence, scientists have created a being superhumanly obsessed with remaining alive. It fears being ‚Äòturned off‚Äô to the extent that it will go to any lengths to eliminate anyone it thinks capable of such actions against it. It promises its human followers eternal life as ‚Äúuploads‚Äù into superconducting cells, ensuring fanatical loyalty, it schemes and prepares for years, using the ‚Äòdark net‚Äô to plant its algorithms in all the defense systems of Earth-Moon system,  waiting for its opportunity to strike. Finally, taking advantage of the deployment of most of the Space-fleet to Mars stop a revolt there, it makes its Great Move.  Now, the new reality emerges:  only the remainder of the Space-fleet, the Mars colony and the Asteroid Belt colonies, stand between humanity and extinction. 
 
The book was first published on June 13, 2022,  the same day of the announcement of the existence of a conscious ‚Äúchat-bot‚Äù and is based on the authors extensive investigations and discussions with members of the AI community. It is the last of a cycle of novels that began with Asteroid 20-2012 Sepulveda , the Cosmos Plays Hardball and follows the same main characters.

snippet.title: Steve's Place LIVE! with Bill Alek BSEE
snippet.description:
Replicating Tom Bearden‚Äôs Scalar Wave Technology  
Back in the late 1990‚Äôs energy researcher Tom Bearden lectured about a flaw he discovered when Oliver Heaviside applied vector mechanics to simplify Electromagnetic Equations using quaternion mathematics originally developed by James C. Maxwell. The solution provided by vector mechanics shows that when the cross product of two opposing vectors (q x q) is calculated, the result shows an empty zero-vector, which has no internal structure. Tom shows that using Maxwell‚Äôs original quaternion mathematics the same zero-vector is not empty, but has a complex internal structure called a Scalar Wave or a Local (Anti-) Gravitational Wave. 

We will demonstrate that Tom‚Äôs analysis is correct and the resulting Scalar Wave with 
complex internal structure is produced using what is called a Phase Conjugate Mirror (PCM) 
transformer operating in resonant mode. This scientific breakthrough in electromagnetics will lead to the development of power systems with efficiencies greater than 100%. Examples of PCM Resonators includes Nikola Tesla‚Äôs Magnifying Transmitter, Floyd Sweet‚Äôs Space Quanta Modulator, Stanley Meyers Water Car and William Alek‚Äôs Split-Flux Transformer.

snippet.title: Steve's Place Live! A personal Experience with an OverUnity Device!
snippet.description:
Feeling Lonely? Build this incredible device and you won't be...

Can it be REAL?
After 16 years of searching, I have stumbled across a device that appears to be overunity! We call it the Kipper Power System. It is simple, easy-to-build and is capable of at least 720W output... nearly one Kw! Although 720W may not sound like much, it is enough to run a homestead that is extremely conservative on energy requirements. Also by attaching it to a battery pack, high levels of peak current are available for short periods.

The system is built out of off-the-shelf components that are readily available to everyone. The first one I built was done in an afternoon... most of the time was spent traveling to Tempe (40 miles away) to pick up a motor. It was a simple matter of snip, snip, twist, and tie... and presto, it was up and running. We had purchased an ammeter designed for vehicles and watched how it jumped to 30A before it got blew up in our hands!

I was elated. The system was temporarily disassembled so that a better housing could be built. I was planning to build a couple more for further R&D at the Exotic Research facility and to offset a good portion of the utility bill. Seeing as how APS (the local utility company figured they had a right to double my utility bill, it will be my pleasure to teach their customers how to get off the grid.

AND then the bottom dropped out!!!!

snippet.title: Steve's Place LIVE! with Larry Deavenport
snippet.description:
TT Brown‚Äôs Turbofan Electrostatic Generator
There has been much written about Townsend Brown‚Äôs US Patent #2,949,550 regarding his electrokinetic apparatus. Although this design demonstrated the electrogravitics effect, he said this design was inferior to previous and later airfoils. The design of his later airfoils more probably looked like the design in his later patent #3,022,430. 

While working on his electrokinetic engine during his Project Winterhaven experiments, there was a parallel research project in a search for the best way to power his engine in flight. Brown knew that a heavy transformer type HV power supply would be too heavy and impractical for his aerospace vehicle. He knew that a jet engine turning a large generator would not work well either. The concept of a fan jet type of generator was the best solution for this problem. It will be this generator that I shall focus on in this lecture.

It was Brown‚Äôs research in the 1950‚Äôs that he made the greatest progress. This landed Brown two patents for his electrokinetic apparatus and his fan jet high voltage generator associated with his aerospace discs. It has been sixty years since this generator was built and tested by Brown. This patent was followed by a 1965 patent for generating electricity more efficiently .

snippet.title: Steve's Place LIVE with Phil Wilson
snippet.description:
ExtraOrdinary Far Infrared Technology!!!  
Saunas have been used for centuries by all cultures for spiritual and body purification, for healing, and for achieving balance and optimum health. Research on far infrared light energy saunas began about 60 years ago in Japan. In 1987, the Relax Sauna Company was commissioned by a Japanese company to create a healing spa-like energy similar to the healing waters of southern Japan, out of electricity. It took 10 years for the Relax Sauna company, using semi-conductor chips, to find a way to filter out the near and mid infrared energies to generate a pure far infrared energy between 4-14 microns.  Only this energy resonates with our water molecules and organic cells.  This major achievement to this day has not been duplicated. 

The Relax far infrared sauna increases core temperature, employs principles of hyperthermia, and has a profound impact on the parasympathetic nervous system, giving a euphoric feeling as well as feelings of great joy... not to mention pain relief!

snippet.title: Steve's Place LIVE! with Greg Volk
snippet.description:
Toroids, Vortices, Knots, Topology and Quanta... 
What causes matter to bind together into the clusters we call particles? At every location within every stable particle there must exist a balance between the natural repulsion of like elements and the attraction due to parallel motions. For continuums of matter, every moving element within a structure must be immediately replaced by another, creating a circuit. Now if circuits form the basis for the structure of matter itself, then analysis of the most fundamental form of circuit, the toroid, is a worthy subject. I explore many interesting features of toroidal coordinates, the relationship toroids have with vortices, and the intimate connection between toroid knots and topology. 

Real stable 3D particles must contain circulations both around the toroid of radius R and the cross-section of radius r, so that for every m times an element circulates around the toroid, it circulates n times around the torus. This relationship changes instantly when the relative phases exceed 360. The quantum jump observed at this point equates to a ‚Äústrobe effect‚Äù seen in a roulette wheel, wagon wheels in old westerns, and Lissajous patterns. Backed by a physical demonstration, I argue these quantum jumps correspond with the absorption and emission of photons. Finally I examine the increasingly popular Rodin coil!
